definition: down/downwards/below/lower/later/next (week etc)/second (of two parts)/to decline/to go down/to arrive at (a decision, conclusion etc)/measure word to show the frequency of an action

sentences.english: Later this month, BarbieGirls will be retooled in this way.
sentences.chinese: 在这个月下旬，芭比女孩将按这个模式重新包装。

sentences.english: In late November, Northeast Field Army was ordered into the customs.
sentences.chinese: 月下旬，东北野战军奉命入关。

sentences.english: Good haymaking weather comes in late May.
sentences.chinese: 五月下旬出现适于调制干草的好天气。

sentences.english: In late June that year, the couple introduced ten thousand tilapia seedlings.
sentences.chinese: 当年6月下旬，夫妻俩引进一万尾罗非鱼苗。

sentences.english: It was toward the end of July, equivalent to the 'san-fu' period ofthe lunar calendar - the hottest days of the year.
sentences.chinese: 这是七月下旬，合中国旧历的三伏，一年最热的时候。

sentences.english: The white iPhone 4 will be out sometime later the month.
sentences.chinese: 这个月下旬白色款iPhone4就要销售完了。

sentences.english: The Law School admits one entering class each year for courses beginning in late August.
sentences.chinese: 法学院每年都招一个八月下旬入学班。

sentences.english: In late August, Typhoon Zita brought more heavy rain to Hong Kong.
sentences.chinese: 八月下旬，台风思蒂为本港带来更多的豪雨。

sentences.english: Watkins jujube mature in late October each year.
sentences.chinese: 金丝小枣每年十月下旬成熟。

sentences.english: Your love life will be much better from mid-to-late November through December.
sentences.chinese: 你的爱情生活会在11月中下旬到12月份变得更好。

sentences.english: This 16-day festival takes place in late September.
sentences.chinese: 这个为期十六天的节庆是于九月下旬开始举行。

sentences.english: In late May Mr. Miller, fresh in from Los Angeles, scurried around the set.
sentences.chinese: 米勒先生在5月下旬，刚从洛杉矶，急忙周围设置。

sentences.english: Implement a home-related project in mid-July and plan to end it in late August.
sentences.chinese: 它会在七月中旬实施并计划在8月下旬结束。

sentences.english: In late March, the synthetic genome started to produce a new form of cells.
sentences.chinese: 在三月下旬，合成体基因组开始制造一个新型的细胞。

sentences.english: Jay Chou' new album is due for release later this month.
sentences.chinese: 周杰伦的新专集预定在本月下旬发行。

sentences.english: They didn’t let me join their group until late December。
sentences.chinese: 一直到12月下旬，他们才让我加入他们小组。

definition: start of month/early in the month
end of month/late in the month
